Actress Jessica Nkosi during the Miss South Africa 2019 beauty pageant grand finale at the Time Square Sun Arena on August 09, 2019 in Pretoria, South Africa. JOHANNESBURG - South African actress Jessica Nkosi shocked fans on social media after revealing that the father of her child had allegedly cheated on her. The Isibaya star took to Instagram on Saturday and explained how she found out about the situation. "To my Instagram followers that came with receipts and pictures when you saw them together... Thank you, you truly love and care for me. Ngiyabonga. I would never have known," said Nkosi. The accusations by Nkosi divided social media and sparked a debate. The father of her child has not responded to the allegations.